text: James Walsh (born 26 September 1948) is an Irish equestrian. He competed in the individual dressage event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
